## .lgo for T1.3 multi-leaf single-admix topology.
## Three leaves (x, y, m) with one admix event (m = mix of A and B).
## Designed to be both legosim-simulatable and legofit-fittable for round-trip tests.

### Parameters
time fixed T_x=0
time fixed T_y=0
time fixed T_m=0
time free T_R=2
time free T_A=0.5
time free T_B=0.5
time free T_admix_m=0.1
mixFrac free m_m=0.3
twoN fixed one=1

### Segments
segment R t=T_R twoN=one
segment A t=T_A twoN=one
segment B t=T_B twoN=one
segment x t=T_x twoN=one samples=1
segment y t=T_y twoN=one samples=1
segment m t=T_m twoN=one samples=1
segment m_A t=T_admix_m twoN=one
segment m_B t=T_admix_m twoN=one

### Relationships
derive A from R
derive B from R
derive x from A
derive y from B
derive m_A from A
derive m_B from B
mix m from m_A + m_m * m_B
